README.md
     1Ôćĺ# Versioning Library for Go
     6Ôćĺgo-version is a library for parsing versions and version constraints,
     7Ôćĺand verifying versions against a set of constraints. go-version
     8Ôćĺcan sort a collection of versions properly, handles prerelease/beta
     9Ôćĺversions, can increment versions, etc.
    10Ôćĺ
    11ÔćĺVersions used with go-version must follow [SemVer](http://semver.org/).
    12Ôćĺ
    13Ôćĺ## Installation and Usage
    15ÔćĺPackage documentation can be found on
    16Ôćĺ[Go Reference](https://pkg.go.dev/github.com/hashicorp/go-version).
    17Ôćĺ
    18ÔćĺInstallation can be done with a normal `go get`:
    19Ôćĺ
    20Ôćĺ```
    21Ôćĺ$ go get github.com/hashicorp/go-version
    22Ôćĺ```
    23Ôćĺ
